      • newQuery

        public void newQuery()
        Sometimes it is necessary to know all triplestore variables of one query. With this method the current state will be persisted. Now it is possible to redrive all triplestore variables from this point with getAllTripleStoreVariablesOfThisQuery() .

      • getAllTripleStoreVariablesOfThisQuery

        public List<String> getAllTripleStoreVariablesOfThisQuery()
        Generate a list of all triplestore variables of the current query. All variables after calling newQuery() are in this list.
        Returns:
        Triplestor variables of current Query.
